Tonat Shar is a tall, burly human, a Factor in the Harmonium. He is stern but fair, he was second-in-command and was thought to be first in line for ruling the faction after Sarin. When Faith took over instead, it must have been something of a surprise. 
Sources: The Factol's Manifesto, 95; Faction War, page 59, 74, 76, 118; Fires of Dis, page 10, 13, 58, 59, 63